@truesandbox
title: True Sandbox

Here.

- @kpd: KPD normalization (50 relation, communist coalition 6)
- @coup: Launch right coup
- @strike: Launch capital strike
- @generale: Launch general strike
- @hinden: Hindenburg patience
- @dvpposition: Change DVP orientation
- @dnvpposition: Change DNVP orientation
- @changeddp: Change DDP orientation
- @relaton: Relationships menu
- @budge: Budget and economics
- @dissent: Party dissents
- @class_votes: Class popularities of parties
- @party: Internal party - strength - dissent
- @forces: Forces
- @advisor: Advisor Action Timer
- @fastforward: Skip two weeks
- @sandbox_menu: Back

@fastforward
on-arrival: month_actions += 1
go-to: truesandbox

Skipped 2 weeks. Current month: [+ month: month +]

@advisor
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 0
go-to: truesandbox

Reset this shit timer. Have fun.

